headline: Barclays Maintains Price Target as Progressive Surpasses Profit Expectations
summary: The Progressive Corporation (NYSE:PGR) ranks among the best set-it-and-forget-it stocks to buy. headline: UnitedHealth Remains Largest U.S. Insurer By Market Cap After 40% Hit In Q2 2025
summary: UnitedHealth continued to be the largest US insurer by market capitalization during the second quarter, even as it experienced a historic tumble as investors balked at earnings figures.
